WEBVTT

00:02:29.677 --> 00:02:33.392
taking with it tax base,
jobs and education dollars.

00:02:34.222 --> 00:02:37.143
The walls made sure
only certain people could leave.

00:02:38.111 --> 00:02:39.261
In multiple places,

00:02:39.285 --> 00:02:42.984
brick and concrete walls
separate city and suburbs,

00:02:43.008 --> 00:02:44.515
white and black,

00:02:44.539 --> 00:02:46.936
running directly across municipal streets

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:48.594
and through neighborhoods.

00:02:48.618 --> 00:02:52.635
They're mere physical manifestations
of racist housing practices

00:02:52.659 --> 00:02:53.818
such as redlining,

00:02:53.842 --> 00:02:55.619
[Denying services to people of color]

00:02:55.643 --> 00:02:56.793
restrictive covenants

00:02:57.972 --> 00:02:59.318
and outright terror.

00:02:59.764 --> 00:03:03.868
In 1971, the Ku Klux Klan
